snippet.title: Disney Tsum Tsum Festival - E3 Announcement Trailer | Switch
snippet.description:
Disney's #TsumTsumFest is coming to #NintendoSwitch! See all your favorite Tsum Tsum characters in this fun, family-friendly party game!

Get ready to play Disney's Tsum Tsum Festival with up to 4 players at home or on-the-go. #BandaiNamco
